{"tid":1156613,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel處理器再爆漏洞，需再度犧牲效能換取安全","createTime":"2019-05-15T17:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T19:21:46.000Z","uid":133430,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8c482d9e1ee328c18950cd519f44612818caba","tid":1156613,"uid":133430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"根據MDS Attacks網站揭露的資訊，MDS旁路漏洞可以用於進行RIDL與Fallout等2種推測性執行攻擊，進而跨越受害電腦的任意安全邊界以竊取資訊，例如將竊取儲存於雲端的資訊，或將個人機敏資料傳送給惡意網站。<br />\n<br />\n與現有攻擊手法不同的是，RIDL與Fallout可以從處理器內部管線填充緩衝區、讀取埠、存儲緩衝區等位置竊取任何資料，甚至包括從未存儲在CPU快取記憶體的數據資料。<br />\n<br />\n然而與先前的Meltdown與Spectre等漏洞相同，透過更新檔修正問題的代價，就是需要犧牲部分處理器效能。甚至在某些情況下需要考慮關閉Intel超執行緒這類多執行緒功能，以確保系統安全。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員也指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">諷刺的是Intel在Coffee Lake Refresh世代處理器導入Meltdown的修補措施，反而讓最新的處理器比舊款處理器更容易受到Fallout影響。</span><br />\n<br />\n影片示範：<br />\nRIDL leaking root password hash<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JXPebaGY8RA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJXPebaGY8RA&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=e0f9b822\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JXPebaGY8RA</a><br />\n<br />\nRIDL leaking Linux kernel data<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UV9GDcOWeeI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUV9GDcOWeeI&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=3331efea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UV9GDcOWeeI</a><br />\n<br />\nRIDL from JavaScript<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KAgoDQmod1Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKAgoDQmod1Y&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=9e487588\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KAgoDQmod1Y</a><br />\n<br />\n原始資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://mdsattacks.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmdsattacks.com%2F&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=50b81fbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://mdsattacks.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n引用來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/70140-intel-processor-explodes-mds-security-vulnerability-affecting-traceability-and-2008-launched-processor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F70140-intel-processor-explodes-mds-security-vulnerability-affecting-traceability-and-2008-launched-processor&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=7b7a3202\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/70140-intel-processor-explodes-mds-security-vulnerability-affecting-traceability-and-2008-launched-processor</a>"},{"pid":"36f630ec32c8059f543823b924cb1e57921528ad","tid":1156613,"uid":131691,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EQgtRM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EQgtRM.png&h=89357efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbNyv5z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbNyv5z.png&h=646630d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8mGEYU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8mGEYU.png&h=77cf8f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50yt4qD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50yt4qD.png&h=dc20d8e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c705546322cbb0e01f2b4d68e5902aa0327b98","tid":1156613,"uid":249885,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"無一句睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\